== HW Interfaces
================================================================
* M_AXI
+-------------+------------+---------------+---------+--------+----------+-----------+--------------+--------------+-------------+-------------+
| Interface   | Data Width | Address Width | Latency | Offset | Register | Max Widen | Max Read     | Max Write    | Num Read    | Num Write   |
|             | (SW->HW)   |               |         |        |          | Bitwidth  | Burst Length | Burst Length | Outstanding | Outstanding |
+-------------+------------+---------------+---------+--------+----------+-----------+--------------+--------------+-------------+-------------+
| m_axi_K     | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
| m_axi_Out_r | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
| m_axi_Q     | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
| m_axi_V     | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
| m_axi_gmem0 | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
| m_axi_gmem1 | 8 -> 8     | 64            | 0       | slave  | 0        | 0         | 64           | 16           | 16          | 16          |
+-------------+------------+---------------+---------+--------+----------+-----------+--------------+--------------+-------------+-------------+

* S_AXILITE Interfaces
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+
| Interface     | Data Width | Address Width | Offset | Register |
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+
| s_axi_control | 32         | 7             | 16     | 0        |
+---------------+------------+---------------+--------+----------+

* S_AXILITE Registers
+---------------+-------------+--------+-------+--------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Interface     | Register    | Offset | Width | Access | Description                      | Bit Fields                                                           |
+---------------+-------------+--------+-------+--------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+
| s_axi_control | CTRL        | 0x00   | 32    | RW     | Control signals                  | 0=AP_START 1=AP_DONE 2=AP_IDLE 3=AP_READY 7=AUTO_RESTART 9=INTERRUPT |
| s_axi_control | GIER        | 0x04   | 32    | RW     | Global Interrupt Enable Register | 0=Enable                                                             |
| s_axi_control | IP_IER      | 0x08   | 32    | RW     | IP Interrupt Enable Register     | 0=CHAN0_INT_EN 1=CHAN1_INT_EN                                        |
| s_axi_control | IP_ISR      | 0x0c   | 32    | RW     | IP Interrupt Status Register     | 0=CHAN0_INT_ST 1=CHAN1_INT_ST                                        |
| s_axi_control | in_q_1      | 0x10   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_q              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_q_2      | 0x14   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_q              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_k_1      | 0x1c   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_k              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_k_2      | 0x20   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_k              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_v_1      | 0x28   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_v              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_v_2      | 0x2c   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_v              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_o_1      | 0x34   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_o              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_o_2      | 0x38   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_o              |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_w_up_1   | 0x40   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_w_up           |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_w_up_2   | 0x44   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_w_up           |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_w_down_1 | 0x4c   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_w_down         |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | in_w_down_2 | 0x50   | 32    | W      | Data signal of in_w_down         |                                                                      |
+---------------+-------------+--------+-------+--------+----------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------+

* AXIS
+-----------+---------------+-------+-------+-------+--------+-------+--------+
| Interface | Register Mode | TDATA | TKEEP | TLAST | TREADY | TSTRB | TVALID |
+-----------+---------------+-------+-------+-------+--------+-------+--------+
| in_r      | both          | 8     | 1     | 1     | 1      | 1     | 1      |
| out_r     | both          | 8     | 1     | 1     | 1      | 1     | 1      |
+-----------+---------------+-------+-------+-------+--------+-------+--------+

