| Interface | Type       | Ports     |
+-----------+------------+-----------+
| ap_clk    | clock      | ap_clk    |
| ap_rst_n  | reset      | ap_rst_n  |
| interrupt | interrupt  | interrupt |
| ap_ctrl   | ap_ctrl_hs |           |
