| in_q      | s_axi_control | register  | offset   | name=in_q_1 offset=0x10 range=32      |
| in_q      | s_axi_control | register  | offset   | name=in_q_2 offset=0x14 range=32      |
| in_k      | m_axi_K       | interface |          |                                       |
| in_k      | s_axi_control | register  | offset   | name=in_k_1 offset=0x1c range=32      |
| in_k      | s_axi_control | register  | offset   | name=in_k_2 offset=0x20 range=32      |
| in_v      | m_axi_V       | interface |          |                                       |
| in_v      | s_axi_control | register  | offset   | name=in_v_1 offset=0x28 range=32      |
